ansportation in city are &nbsp;Local trains and local train stations are available within every few kilometers of any point in the city and the suburban railway operates 2,342 train services and carries more than 7.5 million commuters daily.. Other Modes Like Taxi, Auto Ricshaw and car hire services are easily available all across the city. Recently Metro Rail Project has also been launced in the city.<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p style="text-align: center;">1- THE STREET FOOD, AT ( JUHU ; GIRGAUM CHOWPATTY AT HOMI STREET KHAOGALLI (FORT) ; &nbsp;BACHELOR OF SHAKERS ; CANON NEAR CST) &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;FAMOUS FOR PAV BHAJI, VADA PAV, POTATO ONION BHAJI, SANDWICHES, DOSA, PANI PURI, RAGDA PATTIS, BOILED CHANNA CHAT, CHINESE BHEL.<br />\r\n2- KALA KHATTA SARDAR TARDEO - (FAMOUS FOR PAVBHAJI)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n3- GURUKRUPA, IN SION - (FAMOUS FOR SAMOSA RAGDA)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n4- SATKAR, NEAR GOREGAON STATION - [FAMOUS FOR KONKANI COSTAL MEAL (MIX OF MALVANI &amp; GOMATAK CUSINES)]&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n5 - HIGHWAY GOMANTAK, ON WESTERN EXPRESS HIGHWAY, BANDRA EAST - [FAMOUS FOR KONKANI COSTAL MEAL (MIX OF MALVANI &amp; GOMATAK CUSINES)]&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n6 - GOA HOUSE, AT JUHU - [FAMOUS FOR KONKANI COSTAL MEAL (MIX OF MALVANI &amp; GOMATAK CUSINES)]&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n7 - SINDHUDURG &amp; PRADEEP GOMANTAK, AT FORT - [FAMOUS FOR KONKANI COSTAL MEAL (MIX OF MALVANI &amp; GOMATAK CUSINES)]&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n8 - AASWAD, OPPOSITE SENA BHAVAN IN DADAR - (FAMOUS FOR TYPICAL MAHRASHTRIAN MEAL)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n9 - PRAKASH, IN DADAR - (FAMOUS FOR TYPICAL MAHRASHTRIAN MEAL)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n10 - VINAY HEALTH HOME,&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;AT CHARNI ROAD - (FAMOUS FOR TYPICAL MAHRASHTRIAN MEAL)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n11- RAMANAYAKS UDPI, AT MATUNGA - [FAMOUS FOR SOUTH INDIAN MEAL (UDUPI CUSINE)]&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\r\n12 - CAF&Eacute; MADRAS - (FAMOUS FOR PODI UPMA &amp; RAGI DOSA)&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;